Package controllers

Class GuestMainLayoutController

java.lang.Object
controllers.GuestMainLayoutController
All Implemented Interfaces:
ClientAware, StageAware
public class GuestMainLayoutController extends Object implements ClientAware, StageAware
Controller for the main layout shown to guest users. Provides top navigation (Home / Back / Exit), a side menu for availability check, and a central area where different screens are loaded dynamically.
